To DrAnal- onOne's Plugin Suite 5 is not for Photoshop CS5. Don't let the "5" fool you. I just read on onOne's website that Photoshop CS5 plugins will be available May 31st.

onOne's Plugin Suite 5 has been out for quite sometime, is last years plugin suite for CS4. The CS5 update to the suite is yet to be made available.

Furthermore, until compatible plugins are available I really don't see a reason to bother installing Photoshop CS5. It's like buying a new car without tires. My opinion anyway...Cheers!
